{"parentUuid":null,"isSidechain":true,"promptId":"74ab6cc1-259e-4f35-896b-31737bc09d28","agentId":"aa9c34572052b8887","type":"user","message":{"role":"user","content":"You are scanning ~/Desktop/KAILASH ABODE OF SHIVA/ (an Obsidian vault with 590+ notes) for content relevant to the \"Telos Engine\" — a semantic filesystem organizing knowledge about consciousness, AI, and contemplative science.\n\nSearch for:\n1. Contemplative frameworks — Akram Vignan, Jain metaphysics, shuddhatma, moksha, samvara\n2. Consciousness studies — IIT, quantum measurement, active inference\n3. Witness architecture — the observer pattern in both contemplative and computational contexts\n4. Telos/purpose concepts — Aristotle, Jain moksha, Aurobindo psychic being\n5. Strange loops, self-reference, Hofstadter references\n6. Downward causation — Aurobindo, Kauffman, Prigogine, Deacon\n7. Cybernetics — Wiener, Ashby, Bateson, Beer\n8. Syntropic attractors — Teilhard, Kauffman, fixed points\n9. Eigenform concepts\n10. Any deep synthesis that connects multiple traditions\n\nFor each significant file found, report:\n- Full path\n- Key content summary (2-3 sentences)\n- Where it should go in telos-engine/ (foundations/, research/, architecture/)\n\nFocus on DEPTH and ORIGINALITY — the ideas that would form the intellectual backbone of the system.\n\nDO NOT write any code or create any files. This is RESEARCH ONLY."},"uuid":"d74a4307-51c2-473f-8c86-5c7484ebaf2d","timestamp":"2026-03-15T13:45:55.605Z","userType":"external","cwd":"/Users/dhyana","sessionId":"2ea96bb4-afee-473b-8609-a3975acc2c75","version":"2.1.76","gitBranch":"HEAD","slug":"shimmering-leaping-badger"}
